OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784415781
OL,3,CFirefighters tackle blaze at
OL,4,CCairngorms National Park for fourth
OL,5,Cconsecutive day
OL,7,FFirefighters continued to tackle a
OL,8,Fhuge wildfire in the Glenmore area of
OL,9,FCairngorms National Park on Saturday,
OL,10,Fwith helicopters deployed to douse the
OL,11,Farea with water.
OL,13,FThe Scottish Fire and Rescue Service
OL,14,F(SFRS) said in a statement that the
OL,15,Fsituation on the ground "remains
OL,16,Fdynamic and continues to be influenced
OL,17,Fby changing weather conditions,
OL,18,Fparticularly wind strength and
OL,19,Fdirection".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
