PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784415781
OL,3,CFirefighters tackle blaze at
OL,4,CCairngorms National Park for fourth
OL,5,Cconsecutive day
OL,7,FAfter four days the blaze has still
OL,8,Fbeen burning, but the service said
OL,9,Fthere had been "significant progress
OL,10,Fover the past 24 hours", with
OL,11,Fconditions showing " marked
OL,12,Fimprovement" compared to Friday.
OL,14,FSFRS said the period between 3pm and
OL,15,F6.30pm is "the most challenging part
OL,16,Fof the day", as warmer temperatures
OL,17,Fand changing wind conditions can
OL,18,Finfluence fires.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784415781
OL,3,CFirefighters tackle blaze at
OL,4,CCairngorms National Park for fourth
OL,5,Cconsecutive day
OL,7,FThe service said that it is reviewing
OL,8,Fits operational requirements and
OL,9,Fresource deployment for Saturday night
OL,10,Fand Sunday.
OL,12,F"Crews remain fully committed to
OL,13,Fmaintaining control of the incident
OL,14,Fand protecting local communities," it
OL,15,Fsaid, adding that while there are
OL,16,F"encouraging signs" it is important
OL,17,Fthat firefighters "do not become
OL,18,Fcomplacent".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
