CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1784415781
OL,3,CFirefighters tackle blaze at
OL,4,CCairngorms National Park for fourth
OL,5,Cconsecutive day
OL,7,FDeputy Assistant Chief Officer Michael
OL,8,FHumphreys said: "We hope this update
OL,9,Fprovides reassurance to local
OL,10,Fresidents and communities.
OL,12,F"However, it is equally important that
OL,13,Fexpectations are managed given the
OL,14,Funpredictable nature of wildfire
OL,15,Fincidents and the ongoing influence of
OL,16,Fweather conditions.
