OL,3,CFirefighters tackle blaze at
OL,4,CCairngorms National Park for fourth
OL,5,Cconsecutive day
OL,7,F"We would like to thank the
OL,8,Fpartnership working of landowners and
OL,9,Fagencies and our local communities for
OL,10,Ftheir continued patience, and
OL,11,Fcooperation throughout this incident."
